'''Stoyo Nedin''' ({{lang-bg|Стою Недин}}) (born December 6, 1959 in [[Sofia, Bulgaria]]) is the Chairman of the Bulgarian Investors Association,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://darikfinance.bg/novini/61717/%C4%EE%E1%F0%EE%F2%EE+%EA%EE%F0%EF%EE%F0%E0%F2%E8%E2%ED%EE+%F3%EF%F0%E0%E2%EB%E5%ED%E8%E5+%EF%F0%E8%E2%EB%E8%F7%E0+%E8%ED%E2%E5%F1%F2%E8%F2%EE%F0%E8%F2%E5 |title=Доброто корпоративно управление привлича инвеститорите |trans-title=Good corporate governance attracts investors |work=DarikFinance.bg |date=2011-09-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Yordanov |first=Marian |url=http://www.investor.bg/news/article/81822/264.html |title=Стою Недин: В България не се случиха най-фрапантните неща |trans-title=Shocking things occurred in Bulgaria |date=2009-10-06 |work=Investor.BG}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ebfbusiness.tv/index.php?page=shows&type=4&id=3306&pagenum=20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425232823/http://www.ebfbusiness.tv/index.php?page=shows&type=4&id=3306&pagenum=20 |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2012-04-25 |title=СТОЮ НЕДИН ПРЕДСТАВИТЕЛ НА УС НА АСОЦИАЦИАТА НА ИНВЕСТИТОРИТЕ |trans-title=Stoyu Neddy, Board of the Association of Investors |work=EBF Business TV |language=Bulgarian }}</ref> a member organization of the European Federation of Financial Services Users (Eurofinuse). He has been a member of the European Shareholders Group (Euroshareholders) since 2002.<ref name="karieri">{{cite web |url=http://www.karieri.bg/k3/7773_stoju_nedin_veche_e_chlen_na_direktorskiia_bord_na/ |title=Стою Недин вече е член на директорския борд на Български морски флот |trans-title=Stoyu Nedin a member of the board of directors of Bulgarian Navy |date=2005-11-13 |work=Karieri |language=Bulgarian}}</ref> The members of this association, which merged with Eurofinuse in January 2013,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurofinuse.org/ |title=Welcome to EuroFinUse}}</ref> work mainly with the [[Bulgarian Stock Exchange – Sofia|BSE]]. Furthermore, they help to regulate the development of the stock exchange.
Nedin is also President of the Securities Holders Association, President of the Bulgarian Applied Psychology Association,<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://temanews.com/index.php?p=tema&iid=264&aid=6391 |title=Председателят на УС на Българската асоциация по приложна психология Стою Недин |trans-title=Chairman of the Bulgarian Association of Applied Psychology Stoyu Nedin |journal=TEMA |language=Bulgarian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ngobg.info/bg/search.html?Member=%D0%A1%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%8E+%D0%9D%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BD&MemberType=Members |title=Участие на Стою Недин в управлението на НПО |trans-title=Stoyu Nedin: Participation in NGO management |work= Information Portal of Nongovernmental Organizations (NGOs) in Bulgaria |publisher=Trust for Civil Society in Central and Eastern Europe |language=Bulgarian}}</ref> and director of Vialis Ltd. Since 2005 he has been on the board of directors of the [[Bulgarian Navy]]<ref name="karieri" /> and, later, on the board of directors of [[Swissport]]. He is one of the creators of the Bulgarian Code of Capital Investments.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.econ.bg/news/article127840.html |title=Във всички страни с развит пазар има Национален кодекс за корпоративно управление |trans-title=All developed countries have a National Code of Corporate Governance |date=2007-10-10 |work=econ.bg |language=Bulgarian}}</ref> As a specialist in organizational development and corporate governance, he organizes the awards for Best Corporate Governance.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chambersz.com/a/content/view/5791/580/ |title=Стою Недин, председател на Асоциация на инвеститорите: Банките познават борсата |trans-title=Stoyu Nedin, president of the Association of Investors: Banks knowledge exchange |date=2006-07-03 |language=Bulgarian}}</ref>
